text:
This Lady Discovered She Was HIV Positive At 14 Years, See How... This Lady Discovered She Was HIV Positive At 14 Years, See How She Looks Now At 22! tweet 
A pretty young lady who on Twitter is identified as Saidy Brown (@saidy_brown), is trending on social media after she took to the platform to share how she found out at 14-years-old that she was HIV positive and didn’t think she would live to see 18. 
Now she’s almost 22 and she’s still bubbling with life and looking healthy. After sharing her story online yesterday, the lady who labels herself as an #HIVictor was hailed by internet users.
